text: Tieton ()R.M. Campbell, Tieton: Artist's touch is rewriting community's story in a mighty way, Seattle Post-Intelligencer, June 14, 2007. Accessed online 6 October 2007. is a city in Yakima County, Washington, United States. The population was 1,389 at the 2020 census. ==References== Category:Cities in Washington (state) Category:Yakima County, Washington
